snippet.title: Bill the demon (Macintosh game 1996)
snippet.description:
Bill the demon is a side-scrolling game in which a man-eater demon appears as a main character of the game.
The man-eating demon can eat men and collect souls.
What's more, you can utilize horribly screaming function to break a brick and to paralyze monsters in a short time.
